title: The Who 12-04-1973 Spectrum Theater Philadelphia PA
description:
Hi Everyone,
      This concert has been "bootlegged" before but I haven&#039;t seen any copies of it. I finally found it in a live stream online. The Who were doing their first tour of Quadrophenia. This was broadcast on FM radio via King Biscuit where many of the first copies, cassette tape to vinyl, came to life.
   I recorded and edited this with Audacity extracting to wav. I then used Flac Frontend to compress to flac. 
  Note: There are a few edits in this performance of some words due to FM standards of the time. Other than that, it is the complete concert.
  
 Quadrophenia.......Live at Leeds style!                      Enjoy! srw567
